Key - Class in <Unnamed>
This class represents a key on the keyboard of a piano that can play a note.
Key(int, RealtimePlayer) - Constructor for class Key
Creates a key that plays the note with the midi number provided and plays the key using the player passed in.
Keyboard - Class in <Unnamed>
This class represents the keyboard of a piano that has different keys that can be played.
Keyboard() - Constructor for class Keyboard
Creates a keyboard with two octaves.
keyPressed(KeyEvent) - Method in class Keyboard
Is called when a key is pressed on the keyboard.
keyReleased(KeyEvent) - Method in class Keyboard
Is called when a key that was previously pressed is released.
keyTyped(KeyEvent) - Method in class Keyboard
Is called after a key is typed (pressed and released).
